body_html:
They don't, a partial one would do, but we haven't set it up with two separate builds. We can do that, it's just that more interesting things keep happening. But the documentation is built as well, and doc changes can break for a variety of reasons, some of them subtle.

That said, I do at times merge without testing. Don't tell anyone.
